WEBVTT

00:00.250 --> 00:03.919
Pack up your stuff. Starting tomorrow,
you're gonna go to East Dillon High.

00:04.839 --> 00:07.214
- Kind of looking for a place.
- I do have this trailer.

00:07.382 --> 00:09.300
I'm gonna give my daughter a call.

00:10.327 --> 00:11.510
Don't you scare her!

00:14.389 --> 00:15.640
I'm your new intern.

00:15.808 --> 00:18.309
I've got a bunch of crap in here,
I need you to start moving it.

00:18.477 --> 00:20.645
Why did you forfeit the game?
You just quit on us?

00:20.813 --> 00:23.022
I've got shame
and I apologize to you.

00:23.190 --> 00:25.232
Who wants to finish this fight?

00:25.699 --> 00:28.069
Let's finish it!
Let's finish it!

